myCentury's internal site address is my.century.edu. Log in to myCentury with your StarID and StarID password.

You can also log in to myCentury from Century's website by clicking on Login > myCentury
Watch Century's Student Video to learn more about myCentury at (copy/paste this) link: https://mediaspace.minnstate.edu/media/Student+Video+-+5+-+myCentury.mp4/0_vo0amhi5
